pvn&oh=00_AYAahb6aqZI0II4p0oKSVcUgCO2siejGtPQaO0O5cW8QKA&oe=66E024FF"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "KV 1.png", "id": "1035717108228383", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003240_1035717111561716_4865861407543801459_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1ky45D21k5wQ7kNvgGRf7Xz&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A0IsXKH-Z_mnBwN2-oDopvn&oh=00_AYCobK5Wl7qW6JYiN4bHwnYCIaEGwiHnqaeyDABd6ZQS7g&oe=66E03AEE"}, "display_name": "Track Craft", "keywords": ["track", "craft", "racing", "car", "mixed"], "long_description": "**Track Craft is a mixed-reality racing game where you can turn your surroundings into a racetrack. Craft tracks, and share them with friends. Race. Repeat.**\n\n\n# EXPLORE DIFFERENT WORLDS\n\nGet behind the wheel and experience the 104 pre-built tracks spread across 5 different worlds. Each brings new mechanics, challenges, cars, and skins to unlock.\n\n{2499265100265459}\n\n\n# CRAFT YOUR OWN TRACKS\n\nCreate tracks intuitively thanks to full hand tracking and share them online. Or just race on new tracks created by the community every day.\n\n{1695057567991201}\n\n\n# ULTIMATE MR PLAYGROUND \n\nUse your surroundings and turn them into a mixed-reality race track.\n\n{1272215014134973}\n\n\n# ONLINE MULTIPLAYER\n\nPlay and Craft with your friends at home or online with players across the globe.\n\n{1046525373656002}\n\n\n# BUILD UP YOUR COLLECTION\n\nUnlock new exciting cars by collecting stars.\n\n{850050203892697}\n\n\n# THE FUN NEVER ENDS\n\n\n\nAvailable on Quest 3, Quest Pro, and Quest 2.", "short_description": "CRAFT. SHARE. RACE. REPEAT.\n\nTrack Craft is a mixed-reality racing game where you can turn your surroundings into a racetrack. Craft tracks, Share them with friends. Race. Repeat.\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.gamify.cz/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.gamify.cz/terms-of-service", "publisher_name":